t-of-the-Common-People-(10)','','inherit','open','open','','monument-of-the-common-people-10-2','','','2014-10-21 14:15:13','2014-10-21 12:15:13','',417,'http://192.168.1.11/ANTONSMIT/website/htdocs/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Monument-of-the-Common-People-101.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(557,1,'2014-10-21 14:16:48','2014-10-21 12:16:48','<p>[vc_row el_class=\"custom-grid\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_single_image image=\"418\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"blog-thumb\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>','MONUMENT FOR<br />THE COMMON PEOPLE','','inherit','open','open','','417-revision-v1','','','2014-10-21 14:16:48','2014-10-21 12:16:48','',417,'http://192.168.1.11/ANTONSMIT/website/htdocs/417-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(559,1,'2014-10-21 14:18:30','2014-10-21 12:18:30','','Lionel\'s-Head_1','','inherit','open','open','','lionels-head_1','','','2014-10-21 14:18:30','2014-10-21 12:18:30','',431,'http://192.168.1.11/ANTONSMIT/website/htdocs/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Lionels-Head_1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(560,1,'2014-10-21 14:18:59','2014-10-21 12:18:59','','Lionel\'s-Head','','inherit','open','open','','lionels-head','','','2014-10-21 14:18:59','2014-10-21 12:18:59','',431,'http://192.168.1.11/ANTONSMIT/website/htdocs/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Lionels-Head.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(561,1,'2014-10-21 14:19:08','2014-10-21 12:19:08','<p>[vc_row el_class=\"custom-grid\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_single_image image=\"560\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"blog-thumb\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>','LIONEL\'S HEAD','','inherit','open','open','','431-revision-v1','','','2014-10-21 14:19:08','2014-10-21 12:19:08','',431,'http://192.168.1.11/ANTONSMIT/website/htdocs/431-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(562,1,'2014-10-21 14:23:41','2014-10-21 12:23:41','<p>[vc_row el_class=\"custom-grid\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"566\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"blog-thumb\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"fgj-textblock\"]</p>\r\n<p><em>We built a love and hope it’s good enough,</em><br /><em>just to throw it away,</em><br /><em>With pride on the floor and you’ve been there before,</em><br /><em>you feeling strange,</em><br /><em>when you out of control and you need to let go...</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Broken...</em><br /><em>and I lose myself every time when you cut me open...</em><br /><em>and I don’t know where to run...</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Live today,</em><br /><em>with the love that we make and the times when we break,</em><br /><em>just to play the game,</em><br /><em>When you holding the flame and there is no one to blame,</em><br /><em>Can you explain?</em><br /><em>When up on a climb and you fall behind...</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Broken...</em><br /><em>and I lose myself every time when you cut me open...</em><br /><em>and I don’t know where to run...</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Broken, broken, I’m cut open, open</em><br /><em>I am frozen, my heart is broken...</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Why why can’t you recognise?</em><br /><em>Where is your compromise?</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Broken...</em><br /><em>and I lose myself every time when you cut me open...</em><br /><em>and I don’t know where to run...</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Broken, broken, I’m cut open, open</em><br /><em>I am frozen, my heart is broken...</em></p>\r\n<p>- Words and music by Walt, inspired by the sculpture -</p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>','BROKEN','','publish','closed','closed','','broken','','','2014-10-24 14:47:19','2014-10-24 12:47:19','',0,'http://192.168.1.11/ANTONSMIT/website/htdocs/?post_type=owlabpfl&#038;p=562',19,'owlabpfl','',0),(564,1,'2014-10-21 14:23:41','2014-10-21 12:23:41','<p>[vc_row el_class=\"custom-grid\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"576\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=